subject: Good Day sir,
body:
Good Day sir,
I am yet to get your response as regards the email sent to you for
consideration.
Kindly give your reply,  as your response is very important to us. We
are still waiting for your response
Hoping you will treat this matter as strictly urgent.
Best regards,
Patrick Mullin
Director

subject: Re:   Good Day sir,
body:
Hello Patrick Mullin,

Good day to you too! I hope this message finds you well. I'm sorry, but I don't seem to recall receiving an email from you. Could you please provide me with more details about the subject matter? It would be really helpful for me to understand better.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Peter
